						<td colspan="2"><font face="Verdana"><font style="font-size: 15pt">Le Chevalier de 
						Saint-Georges&nbsp;(1745-1799)<br>
						</font><b><br>
						Afro-French Composer, Violinist &amp; Conductor</b></font><p><b>
						<font style="font-size: 11pt" face="Verdana">France's Best Fencer 
						&amp; Colonel of Black Legion</font></b></p>
